               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; names of the donors; 1st, 2nd, 5th, 6th, 17th and 20th line in the incipit page of Text I; 1st and 2nd line of the incipit page of Text II; one, two or three initial lines of the sections of Text I; the word ሰላም “peace” and its abbreviation in Text II; some words in Text II; elements of the punctuation signs; Ethiopic numerals and/or their elements.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
